trans-unit.source: The DirectoryServicesPermission class allows you to control code access security permissions for <xref href="System.DirectoryServices"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DirectoryServicesPermission gjør at du kode sikkerhetstillatelser for <xref href="System.DirectoryServices"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermission"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermission"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermission"></xref> class with the specified permission access level entries.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermission"> </xref> klassen med de angitte tillatelsen tilgang nivå oppføringene.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermission.PermissionEntries*> property is set to this value.
The specified value for the permissionAccessEntries parameter is .
trans-unit.target: Den angitte verdien for den permissionAccessEntries parameteren er .

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermission"></xref> class with the specified permission state.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermission"> </xref> klassen med den angitte tillatelse-tilstanden.

trans-unit.source: The State parameter is not a valid value of .
trans-unit.target: Den State parameteren er ikke en gyldig verdi for .

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermission"></xref> class with the specified access levels and specified path to an Active Directory Domain Services node.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermission"> </xref> klassen med de angitte tilgangsnivåene og banen til en Active Directory Domain Services-node.

trans-unit.source: The path of the Active Directory Domain Services object, otherwise known as the ADsPath, to which the permissions apply.
trans-unit.target: Banen til Active Directory Domain Services-objektet kalles ADsPath tillatelsene gjelder.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of permission entries for this permission.
A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntryCollection"></xref> object that contains the permission entries for this permission.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntryCollection"> </xref> objekt som inneholder tillatelsesoppføringer for å få denne tillatelsen.
